# This project has no required local environment variables.
#
# - The frontend's Supabase URL + publishable (anon) key live in config.js and are
#   safe to commit: Row Level Security allows public SELECT and blocks all writes.
# - The UPLOAD KEY that authorizes in-browser uploads is NOT stored here. It lives
#   in the Supabase database (private table public.app_config, key = 'upload_secret')
#   and is read only by the `ingest` Edge Function via the service-role key.
#   Retrieve/rotate it from the Supabase SQL editor:
#     select value from public.app_config where key = 'upload_secret';
#     update public.app_config set value = '<new-secret>' where key = 'upload_secret';
#
# The optional local PDF exporter (generate-report.cjs) reads .xlsx files from ./inputs
# and needs no env vars.
